Proberta first appeared as a [[census designated place]] in the [[2010 U.S. census]].<ref name=2010CensusCA/>

The [[2020 United States census]] reported that Proberta had a population of 237. The population density was {{convert|165.6|PD/sqmi|PD/km2|sp=us|adj=off}}. The racial makeup of Proberta was 155 (65.4%) [[White Americans|White]], 0 (0.0%) [[African Americans|African American]], 9 (3.8%) [[Native Americans in the United States|Native American]], 0 (0.0%) [[Asian Americans|Asian]], 2 (0.8%) [[Pacific Islander Americans|Pacific Islander]], 48 (20.3%) from [[Race (United States Census)|other races]], and 23 (9.7%) from two or more races. [[Hispanic and Latino Americans|Hispanic or Latino]] of any race were 90 persons (38.0%).<ref name=DP1>{{cite web |title=Proberta CDP, California; DP1: Profile of General Population and Housing Characteristics - 2020 Census of Population and Housing |url=https://data.census.gov/table/DECENNIALDP2020.DP1?g=1600000US0658814 |website=US Census Bureau |access-date=May 31, 2025}}</ref>

The whole population lived in households. There were 89 households, out of which 20 (22.5%) had children under the age of 18 living in them, 52 (58.4%) were married-couple households, 6 (6.7%) were [[cohabitation|cohabiting]] couple households, 16 (18.0%) had a female householder with no partner present, and 15 (16.9%) had a male householder with no partner present. 13 households (14.6%) were one person, and 7 (7.9%) were one person aged 65 or older. The average household size was 2.66.<ref name=DP1/> There were 67 [[family (U.S. Census)|families]] (75.3% of all households).<ref>{{cite web |title=Proberta CDP, California; P16: Household Type - 2020 Census of Population and Housing |url=https://data.census.gov/table/DECENNIALDHC2020.P16?g=1600000US0658814 |website=US Census Bureau |access-date=May 31, 2025}}</ref>

The age distribution was 62 people (26.2%) under the age of 18, 32 people (13.5%) aged 18 to 24, 47 people (19.8%) aged 25 to 44, 52 people (21.9%) aged 45 to 64, and 44 people (18.6%) who were 65{{nbsp}}years of age or older. The median age was 36.5{{nbsp}}years. For every 100 females, there were 94.3 males.<ref name=DP1/>

There were 89 housing units at an average density of {{convert|62.2|/mi2|/km2|disp=preunit|units&nbsp;|units|}}, which were all occupied, 64 (71.9%) by homeowners, and 25 (28.1%) by renters.<ref name=DP1/>

